title: X-Men Forever (2001 Mini-Series)
description:
Prosh, the sentient ship ,escapes from a celestial and comes back to Earth. He gathers Phoenix, Mystique, Iceman, Toad, and Juggernaut. He tells them the future of the universe depends on them. He plans to send their psychic engrams into their past bodies to experience key events. Only by doing that can they understand the future. 


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
